OL,3,C'He's scared of his party': Starmer
OL,4,Ccalls on PM to return cash from Tory
OL,5,Cdonor
OL,7,FTory donor Frank Hester is alleged to
OL,8,Fhave said in 2019 that Ms Abbott,
OL,9,FBritain's longest-serving black MP,
OL,10,Fmade him "want to hate all black
OL,11,Fwomen" and that she "should be shot".
OL,13,FThe Labour leader began Prime
OL,14,FMinister's Questions by asking the Mr
OL,15,FSunak if he was "proud to be
OL,16,Fbankrolled by someone using racist and
OL,17,Fmisogynist language?".
