OL,7,FMr Sunak replied saying: "the alleged
OL,8,Fcomments were wrong, they are racist,
OL,9,Fhe has rightly apologised for them and
OL,10,Fthat should be accepted".
OL,12,FThe Tory donor said he is "deeply
OL,13,Fsorry" for being "rude" to Ms Abbott,
OL,14,Fbut has not apologised for being
OL,15,F"racist".
OL,17,FMs Abbott has since hit out at both
OL,18,Fthe Conservative and Labour parties,
OL,19,Faccusing them both of "shocking"
OL,20,Fracism.
