OL,7,FShe also took aim at Sir Keir, stating
OL,8,Fthat he "seemed equally reluctant at
OL,9,Fthe onset to call out either racism or
OL,10,Fsexism" and that his focus was instead
OL,11,Fon "demanding the Tories give Hester
OL,12,Fback his money, which is surely not
OL,13,Fthe primary point in this case".
OL,15,FMs Abbott had the Labour whip removed
OL,16,Flast year after she wrote a letter
OL,17,Fabout racism in the Observer, in which
OL,18,Fshe played down the idea that Jewish
OL,19,Fpeople can experience racism.
