OL,7,FHer words in the Independent come
OL,8,Fafter she expressed frustration on X,
OL,9,Fformerly Twitter, that she wasn't
OL,10,Fchosen by the Speaker to ask a
OL,11,Fquestion during PMQs.
OL,13,FShe wrote: "I don't know whose
OL,14,Finterests the Speaker thinks he is
OL,15,Fserving. But it is not the interests
OL,16,Fof the Commons or democracy."
OL,18,FA spokeswoman for Speaker Sir Lindsay
OL,19,FHoyle said there was "not enough time"
OL,20,Fto call all MPs to ask a question,
OL,21,Fincluding Ms Abbott.
