OL,7,FThe prime minister accused the Labour
OL,8,Fleader of "double standards", citing a
OL,9,Fnumber of comments made by Labour MPs.
OL,11,F"He might want to reflect on the
OL,12,Fdouble standards of his deputy leader
OL,13,Fcalling her opponents 'scum', his
OL,14,Fshadow foreign secretary comparing
OL,15,Fconservatives to Nazis, and the man he
OL,16,Fwanted to make chancellor talking
OL,17,Fabout lynching a female minister," Mr
OL,18,FSunak said.
