OL,7,FJeremy Corbyn ally John McDonnell made
OL,8,Fthe comments about wanting to lynch a
OL,9,FConservative female MP in 2015, before
OL,10,FSir Keir was leader of the party.
OL,12,FIn 2019 Shadow Foreign Secretary David
OL,13,FLammy compared the hard-Brexit
OL,14,FEuropean Research Group of Tory MPs to
OL,15,FNazis.
OL,17,FIn a U-turn on Tuesday, Mr Sunak
OL,18,Fdescribed Mr Hester's remarks as
OL,19,F"racist and wrong" in a statement,
OL,20,Fafter Number 10 had initially refused
OL,21,Fto do so.
