OL,7,FThe Scottish Conservatives called on
OL,8,Fthe government to "carefully review
OL,9,Fthe donations it has received from
OL,10,FHester in response to his remarks",
OL,11,Fand confirmed the Scottish
OL,12,FConservative Party had never accepted
OL,13,Fdonations from Mr Hester.
OL,15,FLabour MP Marsha de Cordova asked the
OL,16,Fprime minister if he would return a
OL,17,F#15,000 from Hester to cover the cost
OL,18,Fof a helicopter flight, but Mr Sunak
OL,19,Freplied "no".
