OL,8,Fthat the gentleman is supporting a
OL,9,Fparty that represents one of the most
OL,10,Fdiverse governments in this country's
OL,11,Fhistory."
OL,13,FMs de Cordova said it was "shameful"
OL,14,Fthat it took Mr Sunak more than 24
OL,15,Fhours to label Mr Hester's comments
OL,16,F"racist".
