OL,7,FThe prime minister had come under
OL,8,Fincreasing pressure over the remarks
OL,9,Fas Cabinet Minister Kemi Badenoch
OL,10,Fbroke ranks to describe them as
OL,11,F"racist".
OL,13,FIn a statement issued on Tuesday
OL,14,Fevening, the prime minister's
OL,15,Fspokesman said: "The comments
OL,16,Fallegedly made by Frank Hester were
OL,17,Fracist and wrong. He has now rightly
OL,18,Fapologised for the offence caused and
OL,19,Fwhere remorse is shown it should be
OL,20,Faccepted.
