OL,7,F"The prime minister is clear there is
OL,8,Fno place for racism in public life and
OL,9,Fas the first British-Asian prime
OL,10,Fminister leading one of the most
OL,11,Fethnically diverse Cabinets in our
OL,12,Fhistory, the UK is living proof of
OL,13,Fthat fact."
OL,15,FPressure from Labour and the Lib Dems
OL,16,Fis mounting on the Conservatives to
OL,17,Freturn the #10 million donated by Mr
OL,18,FHester last year, ahead of the Mr
OL,19,FSunak facing Sir Keir Starmer at PMQs
OL,20,Fon Wednesday afternoon.
